high_descs: Turn to the right and cross over to the counter
Pick up the sponge sitting on the left
Turn to the right and head towards the toilet and then turn left crossing over to the silver shelves
Place the sponge on the second shelf
Turn around and go towards the toilet turning left again and crossing the room to the bath tub
Pick up the sponge sitting in the bath tub
Turn right and cross the bathroom turning left to go to the silver shelves against the wall.
Place sponge on shelf beside the other sponge.
anns.task_desc: Move both sponges to the second shelf

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the counter.
Pick up the sponge on the left side of the counter.
Carry the sponge and turn around. Turn left to find the storage cart.
Place the sponge on the center of the storage cart.
Turn around and then right to locate the bath tub.
Pick up the sponge from inside the bath tub.
Hold the sponge and turn right, then left to locate the storage cart.
Place the sponge on the center of the storage cart.
anns.task_desc: Move two sponges to a storage cart.

high_descs: Go to the bathroom counter
Pick up a sponge from the counter
Go to the rack
Place the sponge in the rack
Go to the tub
Pick up a sponge from the tub
Go to the rack
Place the sponge in the rack next to the first
anns.task_desc: Move two sponges to a rack
